title: Discovery of Tetracyclic Derivatives as Highly Potent, Selective, and Bioavailable PKMYT1 Inhibitors for Cancer Therapy.
abstract: PKMYT1 represents a promising therapeutic target for CCNE1-amplified cancers due to its synthetic lethal relationship with CCNE1.
